org.cloudgraph.hbase.io

Interface TableReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TableOperation, TableState
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphTableReader

    public interface TableReader
extends TableOperation
    Provides access to the operational, configuration and other state information required for read operations on a single graph table.

    Acts as a container for one or more RowReader elements and encapsulates the HBase client Get operations for use in read operations across one or more graph rows.

    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
